        How to Choose the Right Real Estate Agent in Brisbane: What to Look For Beyond the Pitch
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Every agent sounds confident in the appraisal meeting. Here is how to evaluate them on what actually matters: their track record in your suburb, honest pricing, and how they behave before you sign.
      </p>
